{
  "name": "AI Product Description Writer — WorkflowStacks",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛍️ AI Product Description Writer\n\n**What it does:** reads products from your Google Sheet, writes a polished, conversion-focused description for every product that doesn't have one, and saves the results to a `Generated` tab.\n\n### Setup (≈5 minutes)\n1. Make a Google Sheet with a tab named `Products` and these column headers in row 1: **Product Name**, **Features**, **Tone** (optional), **Description** (leave empty).\n2. Add a second empty tab named `Generated`.\n3. Open the **Get products** node → connect your Google account → pick your spreadsheet + the `Products` tab.\n4. Open the **Write description (AI)** node → add your OpenAI API key as a credential (any OpenAI-compatible key works).\n5. Open the **Save to Generated tab** node → pick the same spreadsheet + the `Generated` tab.\n6. Click **Execute workflow**. Done — descriptions appear in the `Generated` tab.\n\n💡 Change the writing style by editing the prompt inside **Write description (AI)**.\n\n— Free template from workflowstacks.com",
        "height": 620,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-4000-8000-000000000001",
      "name": "Setup instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-40, -180]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-4000-8000-000000000002",
      "name": "When clicking Execute",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
